tags.description: Ramp Approach: Wide boat ramp points upstream. Can be difficult to land. If river is low, will be a long trailing (parallel) dike upstream of ramp.  When departing, there is a buoy right downstream.
tags.name: Washington
tags.note: Amenities: Full restrooms by pavilion.  Large pavilion with water fountains
